@baseUrl = http://localhost:8000
@adminEmail = admin@example.com
@adminPassword = admin123

### 1️⃣ Login as Admin
# @name login
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "email": "{{adminEmail}}",
    "password": "{{adminPassword}}"
}

### Store Token
@authToken = {{login.response.body.data.accessToken}}


### 2️⃣ Get All Products (Public)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/products


### 3️⃣ Add New Product (Admin Only)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/products
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "name": "API Design Product",
    "slug": "api-design-product",
    "sku": "API-001",
    "price": 199.99,
    "description": "Created via VSCode REST Client",
    "stock_quantity": 50
}


### 4️⃣ Delete Product (Admin Only)
# Replace :id with the actual ID from the Add Product response
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/products/18
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}


### 5️⃣ Logout (Invalidate Current Session)
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/logout
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}


### 6️⃣ Logout All (Invalidate All Sessions for User)
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/logout-all
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
